<br>
Camping in Runneyeye for 3 weeks to get my Blackened Iron Bastard Sword. Waiting in line behind 5 people at Snowflakes pen in WK to hand him the bloody shirt and set him to tracking for the Langseax quest. a 40+ necro camping the barbarian village while I waited who would sell me bronze armor for 5pp per ac point. And hearing about the godly rubicite BP that could regen Hp's. Camping for Halfling faction for a week so I could get the uber Squad ring. <br>
<br>
Most;y though I remember crafted armor. I was so cool because I had an almost complete set of crafted at 28. I was only missing my helm and tried to run to Freeport to get it. I didn't know that they had made Kithicor so dangerous and I was charmed, led deep in to the woods, and killed by some Skeletal Captain. I knew there was no way I'd ever get my corpse back because no one could survive for long in the zone. I was so mad I let all that Uber gear rot and quit EQ until Luclin came out. Still won't play a melee class. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/unyanth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nyanth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(9/22/02 12:07:16 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=21.topic&index=45>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_cry.gif" align=absmiddle>  The Good Ol' days</span><hr size=1> Hi Baervon! Long time no see!<br>
<br>
I came onto quellious 2 days after it opened, and before that I was playing on the Tunare server<br>
<br>
I remember getting rich off of pie tins, and using the incredible proceeds to purchase a flowing black robe<br>
<br>
I remember when only the most Uber druids had a foreman's tunic<br>
<br>
I remember when stepping into the top hole in Lavastorm would make you pop out of the bottom hole (before solusek)<br>
<br>
My first uber weapon for my paladin was a gigantic Zweihander loaned to me by a friend (Thanks Helratos!)<br>
<br>
Does anyone remember the name of the first character on Quellious to make level 50? it was a halfling druid, everyone hated him because he used the treeform/ zone edge bug to get massive exp...nothing like killing a HG at level 15 for a nice exp bonus. The rat used every exploit in the book. And he farmed the heck out of the paw of Opalla quest items.<br>
